span.font: DAG representation of the 21 task, "join" workflow, used in this activity. The initial 20 tasks, labeled "task0" to "task19", are computationally expensive and require 3600 TFlops to compute. The final task, "task20", which depends on all other tasks, requires only 300 TFlops to compute. All files used in this workflow consume 2 GB of disk space. Each task uses X bytes of RAM where X is the sum of the file sizes of that task's input and output files.
